        Selling Your Home When You Have Pets
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Managing pets during a sale campaign takes planning, but it's very manageable. Here's what actually makes a difference to buyers and what you can safely ignore.
      </p>
